api_list.description:
To extract text from a pdf file, use the following parameters:

{
     "url_pdf":"url of the pdf file"
}

Put as in the example below the url of your pdf file.

{
     "url_pdf":"https://halo-pro.com/pdfingles.pdf"
}

Our api returns two types of data:

pages_text_array - This is an array with all the pages of the pdf separated in each position of the array, this way you can choose the text of the specific page extracted.

pdf_complete_text - This return contains the full text of the pdf file.
